name: Katherine Minett
offering: Business Coaching, Business Consulting, Communication Training, Group Coaching, Online Education for Business Owners, Sales Training, Speaking Opportunities
what_you_do: Katherine Minett is a Sales Trainer and coach with 30+ years of front-line sales experience.
who_you_serve: Highly driven professional sales women who sell face to face and must make consistent sales to hit their sales targets.
seeking: Katherine is looking to be a guest on podcasts and radio shows where the listeners are coaches, entrepreneurs and business owners.
social_proof: Winner of three 'Representative of The Year' awards and a consistent track record of exceeding budget in several multinational corporations. Katherine is a certified NLP Practitioner and Practitioner of Hypnosis and has achieved a Black Belt in Taekwondo.
signature_programs: Katherine is the creator of The Sales Confidence Formula, a unique program revolutionising sales training and coaching.
business_focus: Katherine empowers women in sales, transforming their approach to face to face selling.
